name: Sparrow in Morrocan Birdcage, Designer Vinyl Art
description:
A Sparrow sitting in a Morrocan Style Birdcage, Designer Vinyl Wall Art. 

Hand designed and made by Carousel Stationery.

Place the birdcage like it is hanging from the ceiling, or you can sit it above a dresser or table so it looks like it is resting on a table! 

The finished artwork fits on an A4 sheet of paper, the cage measures 10.5" x 6.5" and the chain measures 9" x 0.5". 

The vinyl is of high quality with a self adhesive backing. It has a velvety texture, giving the finished piece a more stylish touch! It has a medium strength tack designed to be easily repositioned, allowing you to easy remove from the wall without damaging the paint.

Application is as simple as peeling back the white backing, placing the vinyl (and the transfer sheet protecting the image) into place, smoothing out the artwork with your hands and a spare credit card and slowly removing the protective sheet to reveal your fantastic piece of artwork! 

NOTE: Our logo is there for you to see that it is a Carousel Stationery design, don't forget to remove it when you place your vinyl on the wall, but if you do forget, you can easily just peel it off.

We make the decals to order and is subject to vinyl availability at the time of order.

All orders are sent by Regular Mail or Air Mail. Australian orders usually take 3-5 business days in transit; International orders can take 6-10 business days.
